    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3147190/extras/2628ae20d6b70ac6cc437994de3d401d.avif?t=1763761900\" width=440 height=280 /></span><br>Join Julian and his friends in this psychological horror experience inspired by point-n-click computer games from the early 2000s. Witness many shenanigans with characters from the infamous 98xx.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3147190/extras/e90453f4cd06af57144d6a6604582044.poster.avif?t=1763761900\" width=280 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3147190/extras/e90453f4cd06af57144d6a6604582044.webm?t=1763761900\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><br><i><strong>STORY</strong></i><br><br>Today is Julia’s birthday and you must help Julian set everything up to make the perfect surprise party for the love of his life! Julian will need help from all his friends too. Visit many places around town and help many characters with their shenanigans so that they might help you in return! Fly through space, sail across the sea, and go on many other wacky adventures with Julian and his friends! <br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><picture><source srcset=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3147190/extras/cce3a23d450658a560a419237ef99e61.webp?t=1763761900\"><img src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3147190/extras/cce3a23d450658a560a419237ef99e61.poster.avif?t=1763761900\" class=\"bb_img\" width=270 height=200 /></picture></span><br><i><strong>GAMEPLAY</strong></i><br><br>This experience plays like an interactive film, where most of the game has cutscenes and dialog, with some minigames in between. The game will change depending on what code you enter at the start. While some elements remain the same, the codes can change the outcome. Codes are unlocked as you progress, but the base game can still be played without inputting a code. Be careful as some codes have corrupt data so enter them at your own risk!<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3147190/extras/a683099339e39e1402251a12de8799de.poster.avif?t=1763761900\" width=250 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3147190/extras/a683099339e39e1402251a12de8799de.webm?t=1763761900\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><br><i><strong>FEATURES</strong></i><br><br>•\tFull Voice Acting<br>•\tStreaming Mode<br>•\t10 Minigames<br>•\t20 In-Game Achievements<br>•\tMultiple Endings<br>•\tUnlockable Secrets<br>•\tAnd more!<br><br><i><strong>MEET THE CAST</strong></i><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3147190/extras/a3748e929e2341f3e03b811c4143529b.poster.avif?t=1763761900\" width=200 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3147190/extras/a3748e929e2341f3e03b811c4143529b.webm?t=1763761900\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><br>Jumping Julian is always willing to lend a helping hand to those who need it. Making new friends is always his number-one priority! Jumping obviously being his second.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3147190/extras/1fa99ea5b08c04cea9f9c8f8b938fe10.poster.avif?t=1763761900\" width=180 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3147190/extras/1fa99ea5b08c04cea9f9c8f8b938fe10.webm?t=1763761900\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><br>This is Julia, Julian’s lovable wife. She and Julian live together at the center of town, always ensuring everything is going according to plan!<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3147190/extras/6eea79ba267ae1851303b32678510cab.poster.avif?t=1763761900\" width=300 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3147190/extras/6eea79ba267ae1851303b32678510cab.webm?t=1763761900\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><br>The happiest face you’ll ever see! Gerald is a happy-go-lucky fellow who never hesitates to share a smile with those who need it. However, he always makes sure that his shop is in shipshape!<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3147190/extras/a871ade30ff706633fb1827fb680ea6e.poster.avif?t=1763761900\" width=250 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3147190/extras/a871ade30ff706633fb1827fb680ea6e.webm?t=1763761900\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><br>Darcy is the angelic dancer who seems to never make a mistake. Perfection is her goal but is never afraid to encourage others who make mistakes themselves.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3147190/extras/6134390553c8e39ce351527eb67fe48d.poster.avif?t=1763761900\" width=200 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3147190/extras/6134390553c8e39ce351527eb67fe48d.webm?t=1763761900\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><br>If you thought pencils couldn’t talk, then you’re wrong. Mr. Write’s goal is to ensure everyone knows the proper ways of writing. I mean what more do you expect from a pencil, right?<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3147190/extras/bd3236a5da069d87abdc8397d9eda145.poster.avif?t=1763761900\" width=200 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3147190/extras/bd3236a5da069d87abdc8397d9eda145.webm?t=1763761900\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><br>While being the ruler of an entire castle, Princess Angelica is as hyper and energetic as one could be. She’s always looking for an adventure and never hesitates to explore many areas in the land! However, she is most proud of her pet frogs, also known as “The Fantastic Frog Choir”!<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3147190/extras/7d8a0da454d843f0536bf4c4e610403e.poster.avif?t=1763761900\" width=300 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3147190/extras/7d8a0da454d843f0536bf4c4e610403e.webm?t=1763761900\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><br>Enjoy yourself witnessing the many shenanigans these wacky characters get themselves into! Let’s just hope they don’t get into any trouble.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3147190/extras/a5a780619323da8db252eb6a686d5110.avif?t=1763761900\" width=200 height=200 /></span><br><i><strong>THIS GAME IS CREATED USING PROGRAMS AND ASSETS THAT COULD BE DANGEROUS FOR SOME PLAYERS. IF ANY SORT OF MEDICAL ISSUES OR PSYCHOLOGICAL DISTRESS COMES UPON YOU WHILE PLAYING, WE ARE NOT TO BE HELD RESPONSIBLE. THANK YOU.<br>-EsraTech LLC</strong></i><br><br>[20][8][5][14][9][7][8][20][13][1][18][5][9][19][3][15][13][9][14][7]",
